title: Bears-Redskins MNF Preview, Freddie Kitchens on the hot seat already? (Football 9/23)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Monday's matchup between the Bears and Redskins (1:00). Then Jason La Canfora joins the podcast to discuss Freddie Kitchens' coaching (20:00), the Panthers QB situation (26:00), Mason Rudolph's first start (34:00), Daniel Jones' dazzling debut (42:00) and the latest on Jalen Ramsey trade rumors (47:00).
